data.eml:eml: Eviota santanai, a new Dwarfgoby from Timor-Leste (Teleostei: Gobiidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Greenfield, David W., Erdmann, Mark V. (2013): Eviota santanai, a new Dwarfgoby from Timor-Leste (Teleostei: Gobiidae). Zootaxa 3741 (4): 593-600, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3741.4.9
